invalid type: string "www.globaliia.org \nBest Practices in Nominating \nAnd Electing Officers and Directors \n\u{f0b7} At the AGM, the Chairman of the NC should present the proposed slate of officers and directors \nand call for a vote.  If a slate with one nominee per position is proposed, the vote can be by voice.  \nIf a choice of candidates is proposed, members should vote by printed ballot. 